>Who would she be?
I'd like to say a genuinely honest, loving, loyal, patient (with me) and generally at least somewhat functional as a person (as opposed to me) but to be frank, I little actual idea. I have this little list of 'desired character traits in waifur' I keep, which includes things like sweet, spicy, perhaps (a lil' bit) bratty and mischievous but honestly, I don't really talk with other people outside of the image boards (and extremely rarely at work), especially about personal topics of any kind. I never was in any kind of romantic relationship either, so I have no grounded frame of reference as to who would I find desirable as a partner. Actually, I don't like people at all, waifurs represent a lot of pleasant sensations I can only wish to experience but a lot of those are physically oriented. I wonder if I actually want a partner at all, or just a fluffy person shaped and sized talking (or perhaps rather 'responsive') fuck toy. Not to mention being with me would probably be a terrible experience. By the way, I'm already over 30, in case anyone wanted to say that I still have time to tailor myself perfectly to the liking of my potential(ly nonexistent) future partner. I'm probably too fat, lazy and set in my ways to allow myself such radical alterations, both to my psyche and physicality.
>What would she look like?
Fluffy, smol(ler than me), feline (or perhaps of other fur covered species, preferably short snouted), with fluff covered flat chest, fluff covered wide hips and generally fluff covered wherever appropriate. Flat is justice, Smol is cute, Sleek is sexy and all that. Depending on the species, big fluffy tail that would be enough to wrap around both of us.
